## Agent habits

- Prefer extending memory adapters + APIs first; Postgres is a dedicated milestone
- Gate write CTAs by role (`src/lib/qol/access.ts`, `canInitiateHandoff`)
- Steward mobile read-only: `useStewardReadOnly` + `stewardMobileMode` preference
- Hub Tools menu in `HubNav` — do not re-flatten; include Audit when elevated
- Cross-local grievance reads: only `union_admin` / `division_admin` / `platform_admin` without switcher; presidents use Hub context switcher
- No first-party `/member` portal — keep grievance notes internal
- Update `docs/PROGRESS.md` + `docs/ROADMAP.md` when closing a milestone
- Before committing large or multi-file changes: run `npm run lint` and relevant tests (`npm run test:unit`; smoke when UI/routes change). Fix lint/test failures before push.
